HEADWORD: Nicotidine
<hw>Ni*cot"i*dine</hw> <pr>(? ⟦or⟧ ?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Nicot</ets>ine + pyr<ets>idine</ets>.]</ety>
